             was indicted for <rs id="t18301209-143-off811" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301209-143-off811" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301209-143-off811" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18301209-143-cd812" type="crimeDate">31st of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-143-off811 t18301209-143-cd812"></join>, 1 sovereign, and 3 half-sovereigns
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18301209-143-victim1298" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Curvey
                  <interp inst="t18301209-143-victim1298" type="surname" value="Curvey"></interp>
